missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-01.md:42:This is a structural flaw in the original chain. Generic harmonic interior regularity is exactly the kind of analysis Tao's averaged model is designed to survive. If the route cannot name an NS-specific ingredient near the start, then the default presumption should be failure, not optimism.
